OL,3,CStormont blunder halts goldmine inquiry
OL,5,FA public Inquiry into plans to build a
OL,6,Fgoldmine in the Sperrins in Co Tyrone
OL,7,Fhas been suspended due to a Stormont
OL,8,Fblunder.
OL,10,FThe Department for Infrastructure
OL,11,Ffailed to follow its own legislation
OL,12,Fby not notifying the Irish Government
OL,13,Fabout the planning application and the
OL,14,Fpublic inquiry. Donegal Council was
OL,15,Falso not given adequate time to
OL,16,Frespond over a transboundary issue
OL,17,Fthat was identified.
