OL,3,CStormont blunder halts goldmine inquiry
OL,5,FThe inquiry only opened on Monday at
OL,6,Fthe Strule Arts Centre but has now
OL,7,Fbeen adjourned because it emerged the
OL,8,Fdepartment officials failed to consult
OL,9,Fwith the Irish Government on
OL,10,F"transboundary issues" breaching their
OL,11,Fown planning regulations.
OL,13,FThe Planning Appeals Commissioner
OL,14,FJacqueline McParland said it was
OL,15,F"deeply regrettable that members of
OL,16,Fthe PAC have been put in this position
OL,17,Fby the inaction of government
OL,18,Fdepartments particularly the planning
OL,19,Fdepartment of the DFI to follow their
OL,20,Fown legislative procedures".
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/5
