OL,3,CStormont blunder halts goldmine inquiry
OL,5,FMs McParland added the inquiry has
OL,6,Fbeen "besieged with difficulties" and
OL,7,Fthis was a "necessary juncture". The
OL,8,Fcost to the public purse and impact on
OL,9,Fcommunities cannot be understated'.
OL,11,FCampaigners against the mine claim the
OL,12,Fgoldmine would have an environmental
OL,13,Fimpact on border areas like Donegal.
OL,15,FSome residents from the county told
OL,16,Fthe inquiry they have not had time to
OL,17,Frespond to it and the public
OL,18,Fconsultation process wasn't "fair".
OL,20,FDuring a tense debate there were calls
OL,21,Ffor the whole inquiry to be scrapped.
