OL,3,CStormont blunder halts goldmine inquiry
OL,5,FOne campaigner urged the commissioner
OL,6,Fto "take the view it cannot proceed
OL,7,Fand to do so would be contrary to
OL,8,Flegislation and natural justice".
OL,10,FA barrister for DFI advised the PAC to
OL,11,F"suspend" the inquiry despite
OL,12,Finitially telling the commissioner it
OL,13,Fcould continue.
OL,15,FThe Department for Infrastructure will
OL,16,Fnow "formally" notify and consult with
OL,17,Fthe Dublin government and also Donegal
OL,18,FCouncil.
OL,20,FA mid inquiry meeting is to be held at
OL,21,Fthe end of March.
